# RevMate Garage - Vehicle Service Booking System

RevMate Garage is a web-based vehicle service booking platform developed using Flask. The system allows users to book vehicle service appointments, select service locations, and manage booking details through a simple and user-friendly interface.

## Features
- Online vehicle service booking
- State, city, and location selection
- Unique booking ID generation
- Appointment management
- Customer information management
- Responsive user interface
- Service confirmation page

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- CSV File Storage

## Modules
### User Module
- Service booking
- Customer details management
- Appointment confirmation

### Booking Module
- Booking ID generation
- Service scheduling
- Appointment tracking

### Admin Module
- View booking records
- Manage customer appointments

## Objective
To simplify vehicle service scheduling by providing an efficient online booking platform that improves customer convenience and garage management operations.
